Alpha
You are here.

A cage is here.

> bob, east
Bob scratches his head with the banana, and makes a sad gesture towards the cage
door.

> open cage
You open the cage, revealing Bob.

> bob, east
“Oh oh. Ah ah!” Bob disappears east.

> east
You walk east.

Gamma
You are here.

Bob is here.

> bob, south
Bob refuses.

> tell bob to go north
Bob refuses.

>
